property.name: text
property.value:
This model models an air conditioner for a one-room windowless log cabin. The goal of the model is to demonstrate a RESTful interface for Ptolemy.
It has two main actors: The AirConditioner models the controller. The Plant models the heat transfer in the room. The unit system ontology calculates the physical units, which can be used by the RESTful interface.
